      "text": "Cameron Ciraldo has stuck solid as the Bulldogs navigate a challenging period, with just one change to the starting side that fell to North Queensland last week. Sitili Tupouniua has been named in the back row, with Josh Curran on the bench, but the pair could trade places on game day as they did last week. Interchange forwards Kurt Mann (head knock) and Jake Turpin (biceps) have been ruled out, with Harry Hayes and Sean O'Sullivan the new faces on the bench.",
